data.description: Fantastic like new 5 bedroom 3 bath home that is move in ready! Welcoming foyer with coat closet! Living room! Open floor plan! Kitchen with granite countertops, island/breakfast bar, pantry, gas range, built in microwave, dishwasher & coffee area! Dining room! Bedroom on main level with nearby full bathroom, could make a great inlaw suite! Upstair loft area! Owner suite with walk in closet, bath with double sink granite vanity, soaking tub, shower & water closet! Spacious spare bedrooms! Hall bathroom with double sink vanity! Laundry room! Washer and dryer can stay with acceptable offer! Backyard with fenced line on the backside! Two car garage! Great location with easy access to Bridgestone, SRS, Fort Eisenhower & more!
